{"id": 6750, "title": "Ticket #6750: A single cpu job may never match a pslot", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe negotiator calculates how much slot-weight each submitter should get.  However, we ignore the fact that when we give out a matching p-slot, we charge the whole amount of the pslot.  This is particularly noticeable when Group Quotas are enabled, although the problem can happen even without group quotas. So, for example, in a newly-booted pool of 40 core machines, each with 40-core pslots, any group with a quota of &lt; 40 will never match any machines.\n\n<p>This ticket will patch the code so that one submitter per negotiation cycle is allowed to go over the limit.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Oct-30 16:13</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=55667\">[55667]</a></span>: Prepare for build. Also, docs for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6725\" title=\"starter crash when deleting docker images\">#6725</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6755\" title=\"condor_tail -stderr always results in an error\">#6755</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6710\" title=\"Make condor_submit -i work with docker jobs\">#6710</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6750\" title=\"A single cpu job may never match a pslot\">#6750</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6731\" title=\"Allow admin to add additional singularity command line args\">#6731</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6757\" title=\"Accounting ads cannot be forwarded by the gangliad\">#6757</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6758\" title=\"Add DaemonLastReconfigTime attribute to condor daemons\">#6758</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6714\" title=\"When surplus and pslots enabled, if demand &lt; pslot size, no jobs match\">#6714</a></span>, and <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6711\" title=\"condor_ssh_to_job -X tries to use ipv6 localhost even when disabled\">#6711</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6786\" title=\"notification on Error poorly documented\">#6786</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6797\" title=\"ec2 configuration file in tarball config directory\">#6797</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6709\" title=\"Improved default configuration for packaged builds\">#6709</a></span>  (By Tim Theisen )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Aug-30 16:22</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=55366\">[55366]</a></span>: Allow one job to go over quota per negotiation cycle because of pslots <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=6750\" title=\"A single cpu job may never match a pslot\">#6750</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2018-Nov-19 11:33", "status": "resolved", "created": "2018-Aug-30 15:38", "fixed_version": "2018-Aug-30 15:38", "broken_version": "v080700", "priority": "2", "subsystem": "DaemonsCM", "assigned_to": "gthain", "derived_from": "", "creator": "gthain", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "tannenba@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}